<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="assistance-n">assistance <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'sɪstəns/    美 /ə'sɪstəns/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>帮助；协助；援助：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>medical / <strong>technical assistance</strong>
医疗援助/技术支持</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>give</strong> / <strong>offer</strong> / <strong>provide assistance to sb</strong>
帮助某人</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>With the assistance of</strong> his brother, he sold one painting.
在弟弟的帮助下，他卖掉了一幅画。</p><footer>译林⑧ – 3</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Can we <strong>be of assistance</strong> (= can we help you) in any way?
我们能帮上什么忙吗？</p></div></div>